= render partial: 'stores/header-search'
.search-store
  .search-store__result
    %p
      検索結果一覧
  - if @stores.present?
    - @stores.each do |category| 
      -category.stores.each do |store|
        .search-store__result__only
          .search-store__result__only__list1
            .search-store__name
              =store.name
            %li.search-store__book-mark
              =link_to "#" do
                =icon("far","bookmark")
          .search-store__result__only__list2
            .search-store__text
              =store.text
            =image_tag("image12.jpg", width: '20%', height: '120px', alt: "")
            .search-store__star
              ★★★☆☆
            .search-store__payment
              =store.payment
            .search-store__area
              =store.prefecture
              =store.city
            .search-store__review
              .review-title
                %a{href: "#"}
                  最高！
              .review-user
                by
                %a{href: "#"}
                  aya
              .review-text
                オススメ商品の三色団子を食べました！とっても美味しいです     
    